"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Redigér</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Klip</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cuts the selected section and puts it to the clipboard. If there is some "
"text selected in the edit field it is placed in the clipboard. Otherwise the "
"selected sentences in the history (if any) are placed in the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Klipper det markerede afsnit og putter det ind på udklipsholderen. Hvis der "
"er noget tekst valgt i redigeringsfeltet placeres det i udklipsholderen. "
"Ellers placeres de valgte sætninger i historikken (om nogen) i "
"udklipsholderen."

